The EcoFlow BLE protocol is not publicly documented; the framing, CRC,
protobuf field numbers and handshake implemented here were derived from
community reverse-engineering projects:

  * rabits/ha-ef-ble                  (Apache License 2.0)
        https://github.com/rabits/ha-ef-ble
